videos.headline: Travis pitches to Corbin for the short TD
videos.description: Jordan Travis throws it out quick to Jashaun Corbin for the FSU touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Travis pitches to Corbin for the short TD) 2021/10/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: FSU DB takes out 2 photographers on INT attempt
videos.description: Two photographers get up smiling after FSU's Jammie Robinson crashes into them on the sideline.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (FSU DB takes out 2 photographers on INT attempt) 2021/10/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mafah busts a 63-yard run for Clemson
videos.description: Phil Mafah gets Clemson in the red zone with a nice 63-yard run.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Uiagalelei airs it out to Allen as Clemson takes the lead) 2021/10/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Uiagalelei airs it out to Allen as Clemson takes the lead
videos.description: Clemson takes a 10-7 lead over Florida State after D.J. Uiagalelei's first touchdown pass of the day.

videos.headline: FSU's Toafili scores wild 75-yard TD after rolling over defender
videos.description: Lawrance Toafili breaks a tackle by rolling over the Clemson defender, then completes his 75-yard score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (FSU’s Toafili scores wild 75-yard TD after rolling over defender) 2021/10/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Shipley punches it in from 2 yards out
videos.description: Will Shipley puts Clemson back in front with this two-yard rushing touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Shipley punches it in from 2 yards out) 2021/10/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: FSU strips Uiagalelei and runs it in for the TD
videos.description: FSU DE Jermaine Johnson II strips D.J. Uiagalele and runs it in to give Florida State the lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (FSU strips Uiagalelei and runs it in for the TD) 2021/10/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Shipley scores to give Clemson the lead late
videos.description: Will Shipley fights through multiple tackles to score and give Clemson the lead over Florida State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Shipley scores to give Clemson the lead late) 2021/10/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Clemson ices game with a TD after failed hook and ladder
videos.description: Florida State tries to win with some theatrics, only to fumble the ball and allow Clemson to scoop it up for the score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Clemson ices game with a TD after failed hook and ladder) 2021/10/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Clemson finds a way past Florida State 30-20
videos.description: Clemson rides Will Shipley and a late defensive touchdown to beat Florida State 30-20.
